rem Harakeyto Records
rem 9/05/2017

do Examine Shop
 [
  print The shop is filled with people searching through boxes full of records,
  print looking for a good deal or rare product. Harakeyto stands over by the
  print register, watching the customers on raised platform.
  setflag seen hara
 ]

ifflag seen hara
 [
  do Talk to Harakeyto
   [
    print You walk up to the owner. Looking down on you he asks, "Can I help you?"
    go Harakeyto
   ]

  do Examine Customers
   [
    print Lots of people crowd the store, so many that you couldn't get in before.
    print All of them rifle through boxes of records.
   ]

  do Examine Records
   [
    print The records are all categorized into different sections.
    print British Heavy Metal:
    print - Black Sabbath, Judas Priest, Iron Maiden 
    print Goth:
    print - Type O Negative, Switchblade Symphony
    print Hard Rock:
    print - Rob Zombie, Marilyn Manson, Gun's & Roses
   ] 
 |]

 
do Exit Shop
 [
  print You step back out into the busy street.
  go Outside Record Shop
 ]


